premise_source_doc_sentence: Leon later returned as the protagonist of Resident Evil 4 and as one of the six protagonists in Resident Evil 6 .
A sequel , Resident Evil 6 , was released in 2012 .
It is the seventh major installment in the Resident Evil series , and was announced in 2005 -- the same year its predecessor Resident Evil 4 was released .
Resident Evil 6 , known in Japan as , is an action-adventure third-person shooter video game developed and published by Capcom .
Resident Evil 6 had a development staff of more than 600 , making it Capcom 's largest production to date .
